org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.bsf.impl
Class AeBSFAbstractExtensionFunctionBean

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.bsf.impl.AeBSFAbstractExtensionFunctionBean
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeBSFAbxExtensionFunctionBean, AeBSFBpelExtensionFunctionBean, AeBSFGenericExtensionFunctionBean
public abstract class AeBSFAbstractExtensionFunctionBean
extends java.lang.Object

This is a base class for all of the BSF specific extension function beans. Each extension function bean provides a way to execute BPEL extension functions, such as bpws:getVariableData() or custom extension functions such as myprfx:myFunction(). This class provides a set of common methods needed by the concrete beans.
